message:
Hi Bob,

I’m excited to present an opportunity for you to acquire this product at a price of $11,000. I believe this will provide great value for you, considering it’s worth $12,000 to you. Let me know what you think!

Hi Jose, thanks for the offer. While I appreciate the value you're offering, I'm looking to pay closer to $9500. This price still leaves room for you to make a profit, and it's within my budget. Let me know what you think!
